text: "All Quiet on the Western Front" is a 1982 song by Elton John. It is the closing track to his 16th studio album Jump Up!. It was also released as a single in the United Kingdom but did not chart. The song title is taken from the novel of the same name by Erich Maria Remarque. ==References== Category:1982 songs Category:Elton John songs
